text: Sune Wehlin (12 January 1923 - 21 September 2020) was a Swedish modern pentathlete. He was born in Stockholm. He competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics. Wehlin died on 21 September 2020 in Stockholm, aged 97. ==References== Category:1923 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Olympians for Sweden Category:Modern pentathletes Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
